    <div class="text-sm italic text-accent">Last updated August 15, 2024</div>
    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        I'm on a mission to find 100 flight schools in the world to partner with and double their student body.  Everyday, I work with the team at <a href="https://rightruddermarketing.com" class="link">Right Rudder Marketing</a> to implement and execute the latest technical strategies and tactics to move flight school businesses up higher on Google search. Our collective goal is to get those flight schools known to their prospective students.  Through our efforts we've helped flight schools in America achieve:
      </text>
