      <p class="pb-5 italic text-gray-300">
        Tim Jedrek giving a talk at King Schools' EDU CON in San Diego, CA September 2023
      </p>
      <text class="text-lg">
        It is truly awe inspiring to see our flight schools transform their operations into large scalable businesses.  I love being a part of that because I know that by growing our flight schools' businesses, it drives more people into aviation and brings more pilots into the industry.  And that's what really matters.  <span class="text-accent">Having a lasting impact on our students and the future pilots of the world.</span>
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="text-2xl py-3 font-bold">How I Got Here</div>
    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        <a href="https://rightruddermarketing.com" class="link">Right Rudder Marketing</a> is pretty new.  It all started in October of 2022 and we signed our first flight school in April of 2023. But I've been in the game longer that just that.  <span class="text-accent">I started my career in manufacturing.</span>  Specifically quality assurance management in the food industry.  With over a decade of experience working in the food industry, I built teams, worked with B2B sales, facilitated federal government and third party audits, and created systems and procedures to build and optimize the departments I managed.  <span class="text-accent">Every quality food safety audit I managed had a passing result and had scores above a 90.</span>  I had a perfect track record.  I bring that same work ethic to every aspect of my life.  I always want to achieve the best and do the best.
      </text>
    </div>
